About
=====

This is the rc.lua my main config script for the awesome wm

Features
========
autostart application with runonce,
integrated shutdown menu,
randowm wallpaper effect,
different layout setup for each tag,

Widgets
=======
Network usage widget,
Memory widget,
Acpitool based battery widget,
Cpu widget,

Requirements
============
xscreensaver
slock
acpitool

Awsome version
==============
awesome v3.4.3 (Engines)
 - Build: Feb  2 2010 06:11:19 for x86_64 by gcc version 4.4.3 (buildd@yellow)
 - D-Bus support: x

Theme
=====
default

Other Files
===========

Notes
====
rc.lua: The Failsafe load, try to load rootman_.lua else load default config

Todo & Errors
=============
xcompmgr is disabled, because of prblems with the random wallpaper
graphical CPU widget is disabled because of problems with multi screen
Random wallpapers don't work with multible screens
